Numbness vs. Feelings

What you get by being numb ///// what you get by feeling

Can blindly follow authority /// Self trust. Having own authority.
Gain a false sense of security. /// Appreciation of self and others.
Achieve the illusion of stability. /// Being present, in touch, in contact.
Self separation, incompletion, /// Listening, being listened to.
-betrayl, -deception, -manipulation. /// Acceptance. Being known.

